entries.title: READ IN FULL: The newly released Trump tax returns
entries.description: Former President Donald Trump's tax returns were released on Friday morning and offer a comprehensive look at his financial records.

entries.title: Philadelphia again surpasses 500 murders, though down slightly from 2021
entries.description: (The Center Square) – Philadelphia has again failed to stop murders in the city, as it repeats a homicide toll that surpasses 500 deaths. While murders are down compared to a year ago, the level of violence dwarfs recent years, when as few as 277 murders happened in 2016.

entries.title: Trump tax returns released to public after multi-year battle by Democrats
entries.description: Former President Donald Trump's tax returns have been released in full after a multi-year quest by Democrats.
